## Third-party code

This repository vendors third-party code that remains under its original
license. The MIT terms above do not extend to these files.

* `harness/vendor/bip340_reference.py` and the BIP test vectors under
  `harness/vendor/` are unmodified copies from https://github.com/bitcoin/bips
  and remain under **BSD-2-Clause**. See `harness/vendor/PROVENANCE.md` for
  exact provenance.

* `kmp/demo/src/main/kotlin/com/appollo41/nip41/demo/Bech32.kt` is a
  near-verbatim subset of ACINQ's `bitcoin-kmp` `Bech32.kt`
  (https://github.com/ACINQ/bitcoin-kmp) and remains under **Apache-2.0**.
  Local adaptations are limited to the `package` declaration and the omission
  of three Bitcoin-specific methods unused by NIP-19; retained declarations
  are byte-identical to upstream. See the file header for details.
